  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increases the price of pan!",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bakery Owners Association said that the price of a 450 gm Irathal pan will be increased by Rs 20.",
        "Also, the Bakery Owners Association has further informed that the price of other bakery products will be increased by Rs.",
        "Accordingly, the new price of an Irathal pan will increase to 190 rupees.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Bakery Owners Association has said that this price increase will come into effect from midnight tonight."
      ],
